Collection of similar type of data which has contiguous memory location.
Index based
1st element of an array is stored at 0th index.
2nd element of an array is stored at 1st index.


Advantages:
1.Code Optimization
2.Random access


Types:
1. Single Dimensional Array
         Syntax:
                  1) datatype[] var;
                  2) datatype []var;
                  3) datatype var[];

2. Multi Dimensional Array
         Syntax:
                  1) datatype[][] var_name;
                  2) datatype [][]var_name;
                  3) datatype var_name[][];
                  4) datatype []var_name[];